data.value: Gharpar consistently integrates facility management services to meet client’s expectations. Gharpar has high level experience in successfully helping clients efficiently in meeting their needs. Clients choose Gharpar for its ability to provide in-house services for beauty, cooking and cleaning servies. Gharpar has fully integrated team which offer services with highest levels of safety, quality and customer service. High-quality service of international standards within a record time is its main purpose.
